    "explanation": "<p><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-baqh{text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-amwm{font-weight:bold;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n</p><table class=\"tg\" style=\"undefined;table-layout: fixed; width: 646px\"><colgroup>\n<col style=\"width: 93px\">\n<col style=\"width: 121px\">\n<col style=\"width: 100px\">\n<col style=\"width: 94px\">\n<col style=\"width: 238px\">\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-amwm\">Activity</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-amwm\" colspan=\"3\">Time estimates (in weeks)</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-amwm\">Immediate predecessor(s)</th>\n  </tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-amwm\"></td>\n    <td class=\"tg-amwm\">Optimistic time ($$t_a$$)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-amwm\">Most likely time ($$t_m$$)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-amwm\">Pessimistic time ($$t_p$$)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-amwm\"></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">A</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">4</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">5</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">6</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">B</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">3</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">5</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">A</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">C</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">2</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">3</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">A</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">D</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">2</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">4</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">6</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">C</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">E</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">3</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">4</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">5</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">B, D`</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody></table><p></p>\n<p>We know that,</p>\n<p>Expected time, $$T_E=\\frac{t_o+4 t_m + t_p}{6}$$</p>\n<p>Therefore,</p>\n<p><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-baqh{text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-c3ow{border-color:inherit;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-7btt{border-color:inherit;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n.tg .tg-amwm{font-weight:bold;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n</p><table class=\"tg\" style=\"undefined;table-layout: fixed; width: 735px\"><colgroup>\n<col style=\"width: 93px\">\n<col style=\"width: 121px\">\n<col style=\"width: 100px\">\n<col style=\"width: 94px\">\n<col style=\"width: 171px\">\n<col style=\"width: 156px\">\n</colgroup>\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\">Activity</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\" colspan=\"3\">Time estimates (in weeks)</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-7btt\">Immediate predecessor(s)</th>\n    <th class=\"tg-amwm\">$$T_E$$</th>\n  </tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-7btt\"></td>\n    <td class=\"tg-7btt\">($$t_a$$)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-7btt\"> ($$t_m$$)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-7btt\">($$t_p$$)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-7btt\"></td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\"></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">A</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">4</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">5</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">6</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">None</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">5</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">B</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">3</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">5</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">A</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">3</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">C</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">1</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">2</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">3</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">A</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">2</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">D</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">2</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">4</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">6</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">C</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">4</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">E</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">3</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">4</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">5</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">B, D</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">4</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody></table><p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m04qjucv/13c81f90-95cf-4d7b-836c-eeaee8138690/5f60a8e0-6038-11ef-a77f-c99d7e1f039c/file-jaoe38c1m04qjucw.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m04qjucv/13c81f90-95cf-4d7b-836c-eeaee8138690/5f60a8e0-6038-11ef-a77f-c99d7e1f039c/file-jaoe38c1m04qjucw.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE ME 2022 Set 2 Industrial Engineering - Pert and Cpm Question 2 English Explanation\"></p>\n<p>Projected completion time $$=5+2+4+4 =15$$</p>\n<p>Hence, the expected time of the project completion is 15 weeks.</p>",
